.SH "NAME"
\fBsudo\fR,
\fBsudoedit\fR
\- execute a command as another user
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.HP 5n
\fBsudo\fR
\fB\-h\fR | \fB\-K\fR | \fB\-k\fR | \fB\-V\fR
.PD 0
.HP 5n
\fBsudo\fR
\fB\-v\fR
[\fB\-AknS\fR]
